text: Gonzala Aurora Bretón Gómez (10 January 1950 – 27 May 2014) was a Mexican archer. Bretón competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics, 1984 Summer Olympics, 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics.Aurora Bretón == References == Category:1950 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Mexican archers Category:Olympians for Mexico Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City
